#          FILE:  A01-dnf
#         USAGE:  . A01-dnf
#   DESCRIPTION:  Sets dnf aliases
#
#       OPTIONS:  ---
#  REQUIREMENTS:  ---
#          BUGS:  ---
#         NOTES:  ---
#        AUTHOR:  Kevin Huntly <kmhuntly@gmail.com>
#       COMPANY:  ---
